Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.97,0:00:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The battle between Tron and I in the Sphere Field is getting intense.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.69,0:00:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\pos(651,547)}Not even the power Astral and I formed, ZEXAL, could bring him down.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.88,0:00:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\pos(624,544)}But I can't afford to lose this Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.21,0:00:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\pos(642,539)}I'm gonna bring it to 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.52,0:00:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.42,0:00:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to admit I'm impressed,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.54,0:00:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,though this is as far as you'll go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.71,0:00:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought you'd get past that unscathed...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.96,0:00:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, that was your ultimate move, wasn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.48,0:00:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With your special move out of the picture now, that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.99,0:00:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you no longer have any chance of winning!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.03,0:00:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will never give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.13,0:00:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not before I deliver the feelings that everyone entrusted me with!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.03,0:00:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And to make things clear, I {\i1}will not{\i0} give up!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.04,0:00:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need such things!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.71,0:01:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn! Draw!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.11,0:01:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the end of the road for you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.25,0:01:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coat of Arm's effect activates!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.57,0:01:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By detaching one Overlay Unit,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.71,0:01:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can use the effect taken from Hope Ray!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.86,0:01:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For this turn, Coat of Arm's Attack Power is raised 500 points,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.86,0:01:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,while Hope Ray's Attack Power drops by 1000 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.42,0:01:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bury you alive with Hope Ray's effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.95,0:01:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coat of Arms attacks Hope Ray!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.59,0:01:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God Rage!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.11,0:01:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trap, activate! Half Unbreak!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.73,0:01:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Monster targeted in battle won't be destroyed during this turn,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.16,0:01:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the damage during this battle is halved!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.30,0:01:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.02,0:02:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now he only has 50 Life left!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.97,0:02:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Persistent pest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.09,0:02:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not done. I still have Life left!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.49,0:02:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I watch that unyielding will of yours, I'm reminded of Kazuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.66,0:02:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like Kazuma, irritating!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.99,0:02:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't allow you to insult my father!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.41,0:02:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Yuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.27,0:02:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to the previous attack, I figured out a winning formula.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.42,0:02:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.95,0:02:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Astral!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.55,0:02:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you realized that Coat of Arms was running out of Overlay Units,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.86,0:02:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and that you would win with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.29,0:02:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate Heraldic Beast - Twinhead Eagle’s effect from my Graveyard!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.39,0:02:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By Banishing this card from my Graveyard,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.26,0:02:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coat of Arms restores two Overlay Units.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.75,0:03:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His Overlay Units...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.07,0:03:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about time you give it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.55,0:03:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set a card face-down and end my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.20,0:03:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,3800 versus 50...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.63,0:03:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The match is basically over now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.63,0:03:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To summarize, Yuma-{\i1}kun{\i0} might have met his match.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.37,0:03:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.97,0:03:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.96,0:03:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is bad, very bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.91,0:03:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Advance, advance, beyond the limits of your strength
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.25,0:03:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come along with me and burn our flame of life
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.15,0:04:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, my friends, what scenery do you suppose
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.28,0:04:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}awaits us on the other side of this hill?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.74,0:04:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, my friends, let's climb it together
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.91,0:04:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's too soon for us to turn back now
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.17,0:04:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The time has come to combine\N together the power dwelling inside me
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.42,0:04:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gotta release my Soul Drive
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.01,0:04:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Advance, advance, beyond the limits of your strength
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.23,0:04:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come along with me and burn our flame of life
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.61,0:04:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Keep running, keep running, until you get there
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.86,0:05:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Once again, once again, keep those challenges coming
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.28,0:05:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My friends, keep on living in the here and now
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.66,0:05:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Keep pressing onward together no matter what happens
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.97,0:05:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Yuma?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.33,0:05:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.61,0:05:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.91,0:05:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My tummy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.93,0:05:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I'm starvin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.80,0:05:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you saying this now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.60,0:05:43.17,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(408,466)}"Number 67: Believe in Victory!\N The Final Shining Draw!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.43,0:05:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really am hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.16,0:05:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.13,0:05:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(664,530)}Isn't that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.34,0:05:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\an8\pos(619,480)}Eat it and be sure to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.75,0:05:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\pos(638,490)}Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.41,0:05:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Duel Lunch Kotori gave me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.39,0:05:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,NOM!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.61,0:06:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's he doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.48,0:06:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does this mean Yuma-{\i1}kun{\i0} gave up the Duel?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.71,0:06:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.01,0:06:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.07,0:06:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma ain't done yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.12,0:06:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.16,0:06:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Yuma!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.58,0:06:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now this is something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.14,0:06:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eating while Dueling.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.30,0:06:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,NOM!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.52,0:06:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.38,0:06:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah! This is your first time eating it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.85,0:06:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is "eating"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.29,0:06:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep. You can't fight on an empty stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.71,0:06:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievable! I can feel my fighting spirit burning inside me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.86,0:06:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haha, ain't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.94,0:06:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is how it is to feel alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.24,0:06:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it goes away, this sensation is unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.76,0:06:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.35,0:07:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has become very interesting staying with you, Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.52,0:07:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's win this, Astral!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.63,0:07:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but I want some more Duel Lunches!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.24,0:07:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want two bowls, no, three!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.42,0:07:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to feel alive again!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.71,0:07:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we're talkin', Astral!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.68,0:07:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our winning formula is set, Yuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.58,0:07:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just believe in me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.83,0:07:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.11,0:07:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.18,0:07:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light and strength, gather on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.79,0:07:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Illuminate the path towards hope once again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.88,0:07:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Final Shining Draw!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.59,0:07:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have been waiting for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.84,0:07:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I equip this card to Hope Ray!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.78,0:07:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth, ZEXAL Weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.18,0:07:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tornado Bringer!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.68,0:08:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? A twin-sword ZEXAL weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.12,0:08:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Due to equiping Tornado Bringer, Hope Ray's Attack Power...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.60,0:08:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is raised by 1300 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.67,0:08:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,5000 Attack Points?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.75,0:08:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To add, the Monster equipped with Tornado Bringer, now an Equip Card, cannot be destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.26,0:08:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, when Lightning Blade is used as an equip card,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.73,0:08:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic and Trap cards on my field cannot be destroyed when targeted!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.28,0:08:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, you can't destroy either of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.93,0:08:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.55,0:08:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're saying that your equip combo with the ZEXAL Weapons...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.96,0:08:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...prevents Coat of Arms' card-destroying effect from activating?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.43,0:08:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.78,0:09:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hope Ray's twin-sword combo is invincible!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.69,0:09:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Hope Ray!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.58,0:09:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack Coat of Arms!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.68,0:09:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hope King Double Chaos Slash!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.76,0:09:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.17,0:09:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.85,0:09:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trap, activate! Blast Medallion!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.17,0:09:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card returns your ZEXAL Weapons to your hand during a Battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.76,0:09:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This also ends the Battle Phase.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.27,0:09:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.69,0:09:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My ZEXAL Weapons...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.95,0:09:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And to add, Blast Medallion's effect, for every card sent back to your hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.31,0:10:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,inflicts 500 points of damage at the end of the turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.02,0:10:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.50,0:10:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Battle Phase is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.89,0:10:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All that's left is ending your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.28,0:10:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means you lose, Yuma and Astral!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.05,0:10:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, we won't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.91,0:10:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not giving up!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.19,0:10:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice one, Yuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.86,0:10:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But how are you gonna get out of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.47,0:10:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.93,0:10:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Same as always, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.85,0:10:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you got the "not giving up" part down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.24,0:10:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's getting ugly, Astral.\N Your Battle Phase is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.08,0:10:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.83,0:10:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,our winning formula is set!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.60,0:10:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.11,0:10:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.54,0:10:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it, Astral!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.35,0:10:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the Magic Card, ZEXAL Catapult!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.25,0:11:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card Special Summons a ZEXAL Weapon from my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.20,0:11:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth, Lightning Blade!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.98,0:11:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.48,0:11:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You forgot this! Coat of Arms' effect activates!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.88,0:11:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It negates and absorbs all Monster effects on the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.08,0:11:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now I activate Amarelease's effect from the Graveyard!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.70,0:11:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Graveyard?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.79,0:11:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By removing Amarelease from the Graveyard,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.22,0:11:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can decrease the number of Monsters needed to Advance Summon by one!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.18,0:11:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth, Tornado Bringer!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.10,0:11:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I tell you it's useless?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.73,0:11:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coat of Arms' effect activates!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.34,0:11:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Absorb Tornado Bringer's effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.49,0:11:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now both your ZEXAL Weapon's effect have been absorbed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.39,0:12:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way. He's out of options.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.04,0:12:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's all over...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.58,0:12:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.03,0:12:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a useless struggle, Yuma and Astral.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.19,0:12:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.77,0:12:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tornado Bringer and Lightning Blade's Levels are five!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.03,0:12:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is set!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.62,0:12:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me those ZEXAL Weapons...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.83,0:12:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's exactly what you're thinking, Tron!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.99,0:12:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Overlay my Level five Lighting Blade and Tornado Bringer!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.18,0:12:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I build the Overlay Network with my two ZEXAL Weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.84,0:12:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Xyz Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.96,0:12:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth, ZEXAL Weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.91,0:12:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lion Arms!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.01,0:12:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A ZEXAL Weapon that's an Xyz Monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.34,0:13:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card can be used as an Equip card with Hope Ray, and with it equipped...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.01,0:13:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,raises its Attack points by 300!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.03,0:13:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this effect cannot be negated!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.13,0:13:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The raging impact from the warrior's golden armor will shake the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.82,0:13:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blitz of Lightning!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.22,0:13:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grant the warrior the strength of a God slayer!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.23,0:13:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Beast-Armor fusion! Lion King Hope Ray!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.95,0:13:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And with 5500 Attack points...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.77,0:13:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you forgotten?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.37,0:13:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Battle Phase turn is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.85,0:13:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Lion Arms' effect activates!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.39,0:13:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lion Arms can attack again when the Battle Phase is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.71,0:13:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! Two Battle Phases in one turn?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.16,0:13:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the ultimate ZEXAL Weapon!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.31,0:13:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But your ZEXAL Weapon's effects are now mine, so your invincibility is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.12,0:13:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coat of Arm's effect activates!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.93,0:14:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bare witness to Coat of Arms' {\i1}true form{\i0}!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.02,0:14:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It destroys one card on my opponent's field!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.51,0:14:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smash Hope Ray to pieces!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.99,0:14:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God Shatter!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.46,0:14:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lion Arm's effect activates!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.59,0:14:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once per turn, this card negates a Monster's effect...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.09,0:14:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and halves its Attack points!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.96,0:14:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.14,0:14:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now go, Lion King Hope Ray!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.50,0:14:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hope Sword - Triple Chaos Slash!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.31,0:15:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He won!! Yuma won!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.48,0:15:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He won!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.83,0:15:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He did it!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.17,0:15:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He won!! ZEXALornot won!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.10,0:15:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He got him, yeah ZEXALornot!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.19,0:15:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma Tsukumo...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.30,0:15:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He won...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.62,0:15:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I give to you the first ever World Duel Carnival winner, Yuma Tsukumo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.59,0:16:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Byron lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.06,0:16:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But none of that matters in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.03,0:16:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just recover the Numbers here and now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.37,0:16:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-what the...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.58,0:16:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.23,0:16:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.99,0:16:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.93,0:16:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Numbers are...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.46,0:16:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you, Faker!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.38,0:16:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tron!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.08,0:17:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma! Yuma!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.89,0:17:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.60,0:17:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use, Byron!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.60,0:17:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your power is useless without the Numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.51,0:17:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Disappear, Byron!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.20,0:17:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tron!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.61,0:18:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.41,0:18:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm gonna bring it to 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.45,0:18:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.18,0:18:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit, what the hell is going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.87,0:18:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma, Astral.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.00,0:18:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Sphere Field is a field meant to recover all the Numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.46,0:18:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.04,0:18:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.18,0:18:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Duel Carnival brought all the Numbers together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.51,0:18:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way would Dr. Faker waste this opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.60,0:18:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So from the start, this field was a trap?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.45,0:18:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Correct. He let us battle here so we would expand the Number's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.55,0:18:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.47,0:18:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.12,0:18:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're foreign objects in this field.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.11,0:18:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, you two will also...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.87,0:19:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.93,0:19:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I won't give up!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.78,0:19:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.99,0:19:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you trying to save me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.96,0:19:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's obvious, isn't it?! Everyone I Duel are my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.62,0:19:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.31,0:19:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand all this complicated stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.42,0:19:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we create bonds with friends through Dueling!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.32,0:19:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And since you Dueled me, you are my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.60,0:19:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.81,0:19:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I see why you don't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.59,0:19:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Dueling goes beyond my desire for revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.75,0:19:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma, I can't live the same way as you and Kazuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.42,0:19:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tron!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.57,0:19:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't allow Faker to do what he wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.36,0:19:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll release all the souls I've captured!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.56,0:20:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell, Yuma, Astral.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.92,0:20:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tron!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.43,0:20:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.77,0:20:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.16,0:20:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.85,0:20:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Forgive me, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.42,0:20:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This time, I will never forget those times...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.45,0:20:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tron!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.67,0:21:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.66,0:21:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.60,0:21:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Astral!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.09,0:21:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.47,0:21:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.62,0:21:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been longing for this moment! Yuma Tsukumo! Astral!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.04,0:22:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Faker.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.11,0:22:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, it's time for the finishing touches.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.11,0:22:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The finishing touches for the destruction of the Astral World!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.50,0:22:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We stand tall, until we have victory in our grasp
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.89,0:22:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Move on ahead, speeding up our throbbing beats
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.90,0:22:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Listen boys and girls, here's the secret to boys and girls like you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.36,0:22:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're really just so spontaneous, wild as can be
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.24,0:22:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I bet you didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.78,0:22:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You might be a handful, but what's wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.37,0:22:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Be up to no good, but learn for real
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.00,0:22:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go the unpredictable route and shuffle your cards with a goal in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.25,0:23:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whenever you feel like you've lost your way, just take a minute to close your eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.51,0:23:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shout "stop!" with all you've got, and there's your boundary line.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.39,0:23:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We stand tall, until we have victory in our grasp
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.69,0:23:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We won't just stop here, not when we don't want to have any regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.19,0:23:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if we get hurt, we can't just hesitate now
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.49,0:23:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We won't just give up, not when our future's a lot brighter than our today
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.87,0:23:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Seriousness... It'll only make us keep fighting even harder
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.33,0:23:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We'll always get as fascinated as we want, and we'll fight on every day
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.97,0:23:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Due to Faker's power, we're stuck in the Sphere Field.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.36,0:23:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, Shark and Kaito have arrived at the collapsing stadium.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.67,0:24:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Duelists guided by the light of destiny will now gather here!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.42,0:24:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the place from before!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.96,0:24:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's going to destroy the Astral World?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.01,0:24:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to protect the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.12,0:24:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are our only remaining hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.03,0:24:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, on Yu-Gi-Oh! ZeXal!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.90,0:24:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Overture Towards Destruction!\N The Threat of Sphere Field Cannon!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.51,0:24:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lend me your power!!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.68,0:24:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ZEXAL Weapon today sure was awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.06,0:24:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now that we've got a ZEXAL Weapon,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.69,0:24:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if a ZEXAL Bell Clapper will ever show up?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.86,0:24:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sure hope a ZEXAL Side Clapper appears.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.15,0:24:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can do something like that? I'm excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.45,0:24:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're hopeless...
